text: Shannon Elizabeth Fadal (or just simply Shannon Elizabeth; September 11, 1973) is an American actress. She has been in movies such as American Pie, Love Actually, and Mr Bean's Holiday. She has also starred in sitcoms such as That '70s Show. Elizabeth was born in Houston, Texas. She grew up around Waco.
